	* location.c: compile fix for gcc 2.x. Fixes #170162

2005-04-12  Carlos Garnacho Parro  <carlosg@mate.org>

	* main.c, callbacks.[ch]: forgot to handle "delete-event" for the
	interface configuration dialog. Very possibly fixes #300226

